toDoubleReal(double[][][]) - Static method in class optimisme.MMCal
This static method toDoubleReal returns the real part of input 3D data the input array must be of size slices by rows by 2*columns, physical layout of the input data is as follows: a[k3][k2][2*k1] = Re[k3][k2][k1], a[k3][k2][2*k1+1] = Im[k3][k2][k1], 0<=k3<slices, 0<=k2<columns, 0<=k1<rows,
